 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will feature 33 riders from 19 nations.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will begin on August 10 with the First Round at 5:19 pm CET followed by the Repechages at 7:21 pm CET.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event resumes on August 11 for the Quarterfinals at 11:29 am CET, then the Semifinals at 12:29 pm CET.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men will compete in the finals for gold at 1:23 pm CET.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britain will be without the decorated Jason Kennyat the Paris Olympic Games as the track cyclist has retired from the sport.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999976626022576, \"rank\": 1.3622912298623243e-06, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Voorhees\", \"score\": 0.5523201010583755, \"rank\": 0.7715365766764528, \"text\": \"Jason\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Voorhees\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Voorhees\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the team field a strong duo in Jack Carlin and Hamish Turnbull.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.985022440562116, \"rank\": 0.010581270755217082, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \